quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,"Behold, today the God-fearing will be amidst shades and springs"
  77,42,and the fruits that they desire (will be ready at hand)
  77,43,Eat and drink and may every joy attend you as a reward for your deeds
  77,44,Thus do We reward those that do good
  77,45,Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth
  77,46,Eat and enjoy yourselves for a while. Surely you are evil-doers
  77,47,Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth
  77,48,"When it is said to them: “Bow down (before Allah),” they do not bow down"
  77,49,Woe on that Day to those that give the lie to the Truth
  77,50,"In what discourse after this (Qur'an) will they, then, believe"